WITHDRAWALDESCRIPTION: Registrant acted as transfer agent for certain unit investment trust CUSIPs in the Advisor Direct program offered by First Trust Portfolios L.P.  The Advisor Direct program was discontinued in 2016.  Registrant has wound down its transfer agent activities.
registrant purchased by another transfer agent, Pacific Stock Transfer Company
The registrant's sole client was a mutual fund that was liquidated in July 27, 2016 and did not do any business after then.
The publicly registered Funds for which Vantagepoint Transfer Agents, LLC served as TA have been liquidated and dissolved.
